lead_paragraph: Phillips scored two of his team’s three goals in a 10-minute span as the Red Bulls rallied to beat Orlando City, 3-2, on Sunday night, ending a four-game losing streak.

headline.print_headline: Wright-Phillips Leads Rally by Red Bulls
